Additionally, the paper involves the use of machine learning and data mining techniques, which are commonly associated with the cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing) sub-categories. The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques, which are commonly associated with the cs.IR (Information Retrieval) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves deep learning techniques, which are commonly associated with the cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-category.
